caption: (Translated by Google) The place does not work, it is called now: filly bar, it seems closed but it remains open until 4 in the morning, many people without masks and without separation, they should close that place.  (Original) El sitio no sirve, se llama ahora: potranca bar, aparenta cerrado pero sigue abierto hasta las 4 de la madrugada, mucha gente sin mascarilla y sin separación, deberían cerrar ese lugar.
